    "Transformer models are quite complex, and therefore interpreting model output can be difficult.",
    "In this paper we briefly introduce the library Captum from Kokhlikyan et al. (2020) (\"comprehension\" in Latin).",
    "This is an open source, extensible library for model interpretability built on PyTorch.",
    "It provides different interpretability methods, grouped into:",
    "• Primary Attribution: evaluates contribution of each input feature to the output of a model."
